{"word":"G5097 - τιμωρέω - timōréō - tim-o-reh'-o - Punish","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">τιμωρέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">timōréō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">tim-o-reh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Punish</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - தண்டிக்கப்படு"},{"paragraph":"1. to succor, come to the help of"},{"paragraph":"2. to avenge"},{"paragraph":"3. to take vengeance on one, to punish"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From a compound of <a href=\"#/G5092 - τιμή - timḗ - tee-may'/5092\">G5092</a> and <b>&#x03BF;&#x03C5;&#x0313;&#x0342;&#x03C1;&#x03BF;&#x03C2;</b> <b>ouros</b> (a <i>guard</i>); properly to <i>protect</i> one&rsquo;s <i>honor</i>, that is, to <i>avenge</i> (<i>inflict a penalty</i>): - punish.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}